Use Case Template 1 :

Name : Register.

Brief description : The user have ability to register to application.

Players : Admin, User, DB.

Precondition : - - - - - - - - - - - - -
                   
Basic Flow : 
1. Click on register button.
2. Register form screens pops up.
3. Fill all the informations of the form.
4. Submit the register button.


Alternative flow : - - - - - - - - - - - - -

Exception flow : Email adress already exist.

Post Conditions : The user will receive an email confirmation.
